hopobject.body: A few months diamox and lasix combination Blerina Uruci, an economist at Barclays, said Britain’s trade performance should improve further as the recovery in the EU picks up. “Net trade performed poorly over 2012 owing to unfavourable external demand and in particular the weakness in the euro area,” she said. “However, as economic conditions in the UK’s main trading partners improve gradually this year, we expect the trade deficit to narrow as well.”
